                Stay Cool this Summer!
              </h3>

              <li class='flex items-center gap-[1.2vw]'>
                <svg
                  xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
                  width='22'
                  height='22'
                  viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                  ><path
                    fill='none'
                    stroke='#DCDDE0'
                    stroke-linecap='round'
                    stroke-linejoin='round'
